# Arduino 1602 Snake Game

![Image showing the gameplay](gamePlay.png?raw=true)

The 16x2 alphanumeric screen was turned into a 16x4 graphical matrix for this snake game. 8 custom characters were defined as shown below:

![CGRAM defined for turning the 16x2 alphanumeric screen into 16x4 graphical matrix](https://secret.sadale.net/blog-assets/Arduino_1602_Snake/CGRAM.png)


Please refer to the blogpost for additional information about this project: [https://sadale.net/49/arduino-1602-snake-game---snake-game-on-alphanumeric-lcd](https://sadale.net/49/arduino-1602-snake-game---snake-game-on-alphanumeric-lcd)
